&lt;li&gt;Ability to write high-quality code (in programming languages like Go, Java, C/C++ etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2–12+ years of professional hands-on software development experience, able to write well-factored algorithms and have experience with commonly used data structures and algorithms&lt;/li&gt;
