&lt;li&gt;Ability to comfortably interact with the CFOs and CEOs of our top merchants&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep empathy for entrepreneurs running a business, and motivation to solve problems to empower them&lt;/li&gt;
