&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to lead cross-functional remediation efforts and track closure of corrective actions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High degree of integrity, independence, and professional scepticism&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in auditing financial controls and operations, with working knowledge of regulatory compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
