&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;This role will be part of the Anti-Money Laundering (AML) Team within the Financial Crimes organization in SDC that is accountable for monitoring, investigating, and reporting suspicious activity indicative of money laundering and other financial crimes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
