&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who is passionate about financial crimes and solving the puzzle of investigations, is naturally curious, and is comfortable operating in ambiguity and finding creative solutions. You will be responsible for reviewing and dispositioning Transaction Monitoring alerts, conducting AML Investigations, and drafting and filing&amp;nbsp; Suspicious Activity reports (SARs) and Suspicious Transaction Report (STRs) with various Financial Intelligence U&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;nits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
