&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with cross-functional teams to address user queries and concerns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining accurate records of user interactions, issues, and resolutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipating and addressing potential technical challenges during the onboarding process. Proactively propose improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offering guidance on best practices, product features, and account setup to ensure user success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously updating knowledge of Stripe&#39;s products, features, and updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalating complex technical issues to appropriate teams for resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Providing exceptional customer service to ensure a positive onboarding experience for users.&lt;/li&gt;
