&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re seeking an experienced Technical Partner Manager to lead technical partner engagements within PE&amp;amp;O. In this role, you&#39;ll own relationships with Stripe Americas bank partners, and oversee partner technical integrations and performance. You&#39;ll drive and influence partner deliverables, ensure partner integration and onboarding success, and deliver operational excellence through strategic initiatives and cross-functional alignment.&lt;/p&gt;
