&lt;li&gt;You should be super organized, great under pressure, and a pro at managing special projects.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Business or a related field is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong work ethic with effective time management and organization skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work under pressure, with multiple priorities and time sensitive deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Well organized and self-directed, but also comfortable working in a team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
